summary:
DAY 4 of my TAYCATION!!! 
I CANT BELIEVE IM GOING TO SEE TAYLOR FOR THE FIRST TIME TONIGHT! 
Already for the bus ride to...
caption:
DAY 4 of my TAYCATION!!!
I CANT BELIEVE IM GOING TO SEE TAYLOR FOR THE FIRST TIME TONIGHT!
Already for the bus ride to Cleveland. I’m just waiting for my Uber, eating my oatmeal, trying not to explode. I have a fun day around Cleveland planned and then the best night ever.

I will be in Sec E, Row 29, Seat 12 and as much as I am trying not to hope, I do really hope I get to meet Tay. Even if I don’t it will be a magical night!

@taylorswift @taylornation
